                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9423" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2350</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">984 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">酿造更美好的现在和未来：重庆啤酒的ESG践行之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Brewing a Better Present and Future: The ESG Practice of Chongqing Beer</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蒋秋菊，胡雨潇，张雪珂</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆啤酒股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆啤酒；ESG；ESG报告</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Chongqing Beer；ESG；ESG report</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在加快发展新质生产力、积极推动绿色低碳经济成为国家战略的时代背景下，关注并践行ESG理念，既是企业责无旁贷的历史任务，也是区域经济不断塑造发展新动能与新优势、促进社会生产力实现新跃升的历史机遇。重庆啤酒作为国内知名的啤酒生产企业，2023年首次披露ESG报告，积极响应ESG理念。本篇案例以重庆啤酒实施ESG理念为核心的可持续发展战略为主线，围绕其制定的“共同迈向并超越零目标”ESG计划，详细描述了重庆啤酒如何践行ESG理念以及践行ESG理念取得的效果。通过对该案例的深入挖掘， 希望能够帮助学生了解ESG管理模式、ESG实质性议题ESG与可持续发展理论等知识点，引发学生对ESG 相关问题的思考和讨论，培养学生运用管理知识进行分析问题、解决问题的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Under the background of accelerating the development of new productivity and actively promoting green and low-carbon economy as a national strategy, paying attention to and practicing the ESG concept is not only a historical task for enterprises, but also a historical opportunity for regional economy to continuously shape new driving forces and advantages for development and promote the new leap of social productivity. As a well-known beer production enterprise in China, Chongqing Beer first disclosed the ESG report in 2023, which actively responded to the ESG concept. This case takes Chongqing Beer &#39;s sustainable development strategy with the implementation of ESG concept as the core as the main line, and focuses on its ESG plan of &quot; moving towards and exceeding the zero goal together. &quot; It describes in detail how Chongqing Beer practices the ESG concept and the effect of practicing the ESG concept. Through the in-depth excavation of the case, we hope to help students understand the knowledge points of ESG management mode, ESG substantive issues ESG and sustainable development theory, trigger students &#39; thinking and discussion on ESG-related issues, and cultivate students &#39; ability to use management knowledge to analyze and solve problems.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG的概念;PEST分析;ESG管理模式;ESG与三重底线理论;ESG与可持续发展理论;信号传递理论;利益相关者理论;共享价值;战略一致性理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
